      • getBucket

        public final int getBucket()
        Gets the traffic quality bucket, which is a value between 0 and 3.

        The following table describes the traffic quality bucket values:

        ValueDescriptionTravel Time
        0Stop and goGreater than 175% of free flow traffic time.
        1HeavyBetween 150% and 175% of free flow traffic time.
        2ModerateBetween 125% and 150% of free flow traffic time.
        3Free flowLess than 125% of free flow traffic time.
        Returns:
        Traffic quality bucket or Integer#MIN_VALUE if information is not available.
